trans-unit.source: Represents request objects submitted as a batch to [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/add/includes/ssastoria-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Representa pedido objetos submetidos como um lote para [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/add/includes/ssastoria-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: In a group of queries submitted as a batch to the data service, the queries are specified as DataServiceRequest instances.
trans-unit.target: Um grupo de consultas submetidas como um lote para o serviço de dados, as consultas são especificadas como DataServiceRequest instâncias.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> is returned that represents the response of the batch request as a whole.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>é devolvido que representa a resposta do pedido de batch, como um todo.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>

trans-unit.source: Individual query responses are represented as <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.QueryOperationResponse> objects, derived from <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.OperationResponse>, that are accessible by enumerating the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> instance.
trans-unit.target: Respostas de consulta individuais são representadas como <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.QueryOperationResponse>objetos, derivados <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.OperationResponse>, que estão acessíveis através da enumeração de <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>instância.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.OperationResponse> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.QueryOperationResponse>

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of object submitted as a batch to the data service.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o tipo de objeto submetido como um lote para o serviço de dados.

trans-unit.source: Gets the URI of the request object submitted to a data service.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o URI do objeto pedido submetido para um serviço de dados.

trans-unit.source: Represents the URI of the query to the data service.
trans-unit.target: Representa o URI da consulta para o serviço de dados.

trans-unit.source: The requested URI as a <xref:System.String> value.
trans-unit.target: O URI de pedido como um <xref:System.String>valor.</xref:System.String>
